\ls5\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 In those days people who were blameless in the eyes of God were thought to have the blessing of God. \'a0But they didn\'92t feel it.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 We talked a little bit\'a0about\'a0this last week.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The world tells us the same thing today\'85we expect when we do good for God, God will do good for us.\uc0\u8232 \
